item.title: about
item.description:
My name is Jesús and I am originally from Venezuela. I am frontend web developer with more than 3 years of experience and highly skilled in web front-end technologies. I can develop fast, responsive, high quality & user friendly clients with your goals in mind.

Most of my experience resolves around working with e-commerce platform, developing dashboards for web apps and JavaScript plugins.
